OL,3,CPackaging tax will push up prices for
OL,4,Cconsumers, say industry bosses
OL,6,FMore than 80% of the cost of the new
OL,7,Fpackaging tax is likely to be passed
OL,8,Fon consumers, industry leaders have
OL,9,Fwarned.
OL,11,FThe new tax ` or the extended producer
OL,12,Fresponsibility (EPR) scheme, for which
OL,13,Ffirms must submit their latest data on
OL,14,Fthe packaging they have used by
OL,15,FOctober 1 ` is likely to place a
OL,16,F"significant financial burden" on UK
OL,17,Fretailers and households, a survey of
OL,18,Fleading retailers for the British
OL,19,FRetail Consortium (BRC) suggests.
