OL,3,CPackaging tax will push up prices for
OL,4,Cconsumers, say industry bosses
OL,6,FThe BRC said the industry had been
OL,7,Fleft little room to absorb any extra
OL,8,Fcosts following last year's budget,
OL,9,Fwhen retailers were hit with #5
OL,10,Fbillion in extra employment costs due
OL,11,Fto higher employer national insurance
OL,12,Fcontributions and the rising national
OL,13,Fliving wage.
OL,15,FIt said the EPR, set to cost industry
OL,16,Fbillions, would be "yet another
OL,17,Finflationary pressure" when food
OL,18,Fprices were already rising fast, with
OL,19,Fthe Bank of England estimating that
OL,20,Fthe policy alone will add 0.5% to food
OL,21,Finflation.
