OL,3,CPackaging tax will push up prices for
OL,4,Cconsumers, say industry bosses
OL,6,FIn addition to the financial impact,
OL,7,Fsome 85% of retailers said the
OL,8,Fadministrative and compliance burden
OL,9,Fthey faced had increased significantly
OL,10,Fas a result of EPR.
OL,12,FFirms are required to report extensive
OL,13,Finformation on the composition and
OL,14,Famounts of packaging they are putting
OL,15,Fon the market.
OL,17,FThe tax is levied on any company which
OL,18,Fproduces packaging bought and disposed
OL,19,Fof by households, and includes
OL,20,Fretailers and brands.
